params._collateralAddress: The collateral asset used by collateral vault.
params._liqLTV: The LTV that the user wants to use for their collateral vault.
params._targetVault: The target vault used for the borrow by collateral vault.

doCall(address,uint256,bytes).details: VaultManager is an owner/admin of many contracts in the Twyne system.This function helps Governance in case a specific a specific external function call was not implemented.

params._collateralAddress: the collateral asset held by the intermediate vault.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

params._index: The index at which this _targetVault is stored in `allowedTargetVaultList`.
params._targetVault: The target vault that should be allowed for the intermediate vault.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

params._targetVault: The target vault that should be allowed for the intermediate vault.

params._rampDuration: ramp duration in seconds (0 for immediate effect) during which the liquidation LTV will change.

setOracleResolvedVault(address,bool).details: called by createCollateralVault() when a new collateral vault is created so collateral can be price properly.Configures the collateral vault to use internal pricing via `convertToAssets()`.

params._allow: bool value to pass to govSetResolvedVault. True to configure the vault, false to clear the record.
params._vault: EVK or collateral vault address. Must implement `convertToAssets()`.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

checkLiqLTV(uint256,address,address).notice: Checks that the user-set LTV is within the min and max bounds.

doCall(address,uint256,bytes).notice: Perform an arbitrary external call. Governance-only.

getIntermediateVault(address).notice: Get a collateral vault's intermediate vault.

removeAllowedTargetVault(address,address.notice: Remove an allowed target vault for a specific intermediate vault. Governance-only.

setAllowedTargetVault(address,address).notice: Set an allowed target vault for a specific intermediate vault. Governance-only.

setIntermediateVault(address).notice: Set a collateral vault's intermediate vault. Governance-only.

setLTV(address,address,uint16,uint16,uin.notice: Set new LTV values for an intermediate vault by calling EVK.setLTV(). Callable by governance or collateral vault factory.

setOracleResolvedVault(address,bool).notice: Set new oracleRouter resolved vault value. Callable by governance or collateral vault factory.

targetVaultLength(address).notice: Return the length of allowedTargetVaultList. Useful for frontend.
